It is a more manageable tribe. It's closer to the [Dunbar number](!Wikipedia), which still applies online[^twitter]. Even if I'm on the bottom of the Wikipedia heap, that's fine. As long as I know where I am! I don't have to be a rich elite to be happy; a master craftsman is content[^prole], and "a cat may look at a king".

